  <h1 id="Microsoft_Xna_Framework_Audio_Cue_Apply3D_" data-uid="Microsoft.Xna.Framework.Audio.Cue.Apply3D*" class="text-break">.Cue.Apply3D(AudioListener, AudioEmitter) Method</h1>

