    <div class="markdown level0 summary"><p>Updates the simulated 3D Audio settings calculated between an AudioEmitter and AudioListener.</p>
</div>
    <div class="markdown level0 conceptual"></div>
    
      
        <div class="codewrapper">
          <pre><code class="lang-csharp hljs">public void Apply3D(AudioListener listener, AudioEmitter emitter)</code></pre>
        </div>
      
      
      
      
      
      
