    <h id="Microsoft_Xna_Framework_Audio_Cue_Apply3D_Microsoft_Xna_Framework_Audio_AudioListener_Microsoft_Xna_Framework_Audio_AudioEmitter__remarks">Remarks</h>
    <div class="markdown level0 remarks"><p>This must be called before Play().</p>
<p>Calling this method automatically converts the sound to monoaural and sets the speaker mix for any sound played by this cue to a value calculated with the listener&apos;s and emitter&apos;s positions. Any stereo information in the sound will be discarded.</p>
